comment: Jordan (LAC) makes incidental contact with Morris (PHO) that does not affect his layup attempt.
Paul (LAC) shoves Morris (PHO) during his layup attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Morris (PHO) changes his pivot foot on the spin move.
Paul (LAC) wraps up Morris (PHO) on his drive to the basket.
Chandler (PHO) affects Jordan's (LAC) FOM as he attempts to set a screen on the perimeter.
Chandler (PHO) sets the screen on Rivers (LAC) and gives him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
Price (PHO) makes body to body contact with Griffin (LAC) while trying to intercept the pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Tucker (PHO) makes incidental contact with Jordan (LAC) during the rebound attempt.
Chandler (PHO) deflects the inbound pass into the backcourt.
Chandler (PHO) wraps Griffin (LAC) around the waist and affects his ability to secure the inbound pass.
Jordan (LAC) makes contact with Bledsoe's (PHO) body that affects his drive to the basket and layup attempt.
Chandler (PHO) commits a take foul on Paul (LAC).
Paul (LAC) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Knight's (PHO) jump shot.
